settings.heading: WELCOME TO MOULDINGS, CORBELS & MORE
settings.subheading:
Mouldings, Corbels and More was created for the trade design enthusiast and DIY hobbyist that is searching for an eclectic mix of beautiful interior products for their next remodel or new construction project. We’ve search for those hard to find niche products from national and international manufacturers and provide them to you at a competitive price with FREE shipping on most brands. We love these products and we think you will as well.

If you haven’t signed up for our Mailing List or aren’t following us on  Facebook, Twitter or Instagram, maybe it’s time to start. We regularly post application photos of the products we offer incorporated into beautiful environments on Instagram.
